response.overview: This third volume of NICK JR. FAVORITES offers a collection of the best episodes from six of Nickelodeon's most popular shows: DORA THE EXPLORER's "Meet Diego;" THE BACKYARDIGANS' "Race to the Tower of Power;" BLUE'S CLUES' "Joe's Surprise Party;" LAZYTOWN's "Soccer Sucker;" LITTLE BILL's "Same Moon, Same Sun, Same Star" and "All Together Now;" and MAX & RUBY's "Ruby's Pajama Party," "Baby Max," and "Bunny Scout Brownies."
response.title: Nick Jr. Favorites - Vol. 3
